data.Title: (EXPLOSIVE HAZARD) IED EXPLOSION RPT  Hokmati Gizab
data.Summary: ON 17 MARCH 2017 AT 0834 THE 32ND POLICE DISTRICT DISPATCHED AN 8 MAN FOOT PATROL FROM THE PROVINCIAL HQ. WHILE MINGLING AMONGST THE ECHO VILLAGE YOUTH, 4 OF THE LOCAL POLICE OFFICERS RETREATED INTO AN ABANDONED BUILDING AND REPORTEDLY FORCED (1) 8 YEAR OLD LN MALE TO DRESS UP IN LITTLE GIRL CLOTHES AND DANCE AROUND WHILE BEING FILMED. SIMULTANEOUSLY, 9 INS WERE SETTING UP (3) CWIEDS IVO OF THE ABANDONED BUILDING. PRIOR TO THE INS COMPLETING THEIR WORK THE (4) REMAINING LP OFFICERS LOCATED ACROSS THE STREET INTERRUPTED THE INS ACTIVITY AND AS A RESULT (1) INS SVEST DETONATED RESULTING IN (1) WIA AND (1) KIA LP OFFICER. DURING THE ENSUING FIREFIGHT, INS SUFFERED (2) KIA AND (5) WIA. NFI. EOD WAS ALERTED ABOUT THE 3 X CWIEDs AND THEY CAME AND CLEARED THEM.

data.Title: (EXPLOSIVE HAZARD) IED EXPLOSION RPT  Ghoryan
data.Summary: ON 121304APR2017, THE LOCAL ARMY WAS ATTACKED BY A SVBIED AT CHECKPOINT AT THE WESTERN END OF ROUTE IMAGINARY.  IMMEDIATELY FOLLOWING THE SVBIED EXPLOSION, TEAM WAS ENGAGED FROM 6 SURROUNDING FIRING POINTS WITH SAF.  SAF ATTACK CONTINUES FOR 13 MINUTES.  NO LOCAL SOLDIERS WERE INJURED IN THE ATTACK.  ONE LOCAL ARMY SUV SUSTAINED A FLAT TIRE FROM A RICOCHETING BULLET.  ATTACKERS RAN OUT OF AMMUNITION, DROPPED THEIR WEAPONS AND FLED INTO THE DESERT ON DONKEYS.  TEAM COULD NOT PURSUE DUE TO FLAT TIRE.

data.Summary: ON 28 FEB 2019 AT APPROXIMATELY 1545,  A TOYOTA LAND CRUISER APPROACHED THE COP ECP MGRS: 42SWD1783918515 CARRYING 5X LOCAL NATIONALS. data.Title: (EXPLOSIVE HAZARD) IED EXPLOSION RPT  Baghran
data.Summary: ON 140700MAR2017 IN BAGHRAN, HELMAND PROVINCE, INS FIGHTERS ATTACKED A DISMOUNTED PATROL OF COALITION AND LOCAL ARMY SOLDIERS VIA THREE PBIED'S.  COALITION FORCES OBSERVED THE THREE SUICIDE BOMBERS RUNNING TOWARDS THE PATROL GROUP SCREAMING AND WAVING THEIR HANDS.  THE THREE SUICIDE BOMBERS WERE RUNNING ONE BEHIND THE OTHER IN A STRAIGHT LINE.  THE FIRST SUICIDE BOMBER TRIPPED ON A ROCK AND FELL TO THE GROUND.  THE OTHER TWO SUICIDE BOMBERS THEN TRIPPED OVER THE FIRST SUICIDE BOMBER AND FELL TO THE GROUND AS WELL.  UPON FALLING TO THE GROUND ALL THREE PBIED'S DETONATED RESULTING IN 3 ENEMY KIA.  NO COALITION OR ANSF WERE INJURED OR KILLED.

data.Title: (ENEMY ACTION) DIRECT FIRE RPT  Chaki Wardak
data.Summary: ON 112309JUN2017, AN INS COMMANDER WAS CONFIRMED KILLED TODAY AS A RESULT OF A RECENT OPERATION BY AFGHAN COMMANDOS, NATIONAL POLICE, NATIONAL ARMY AND COALITION FORCES IN CHAK DISTRICT, WARDAK PROVINCE. THE INS COMMANDER, AHMAD IBRAHIMI, COMMANDED AN INSURGENT CELL, SPECIALIZING IN IED EMPLACEMENT AND ASSASSINATIONS. COALITION FORCES SAID AHMAD IBRAHIMI WAS RESPONSIBLE FOR THE ASSASSINATION OF CHAK-E WARDAK DISTRICT GOVERNOR MOHAMMAD ISMAIL WAFA AND HIS SON, WHO WERE GUNNED DOWN IN A CAR IN JULY AS THEY TRAVELED TO THE GOVERNOR'S OFFICE. AHMAD IBRAHIMI IS ALSO BELIEVED TO BE RESPONSIBLE FOR THE DEATHS AND INJURIES OF SEVERAL AFGHAN CIVILIANS, KILLED BY IEDS PLANTED BY HIS CELL. THE RECENT OPERATION IN WARDAK, ACCORDING TO AFGHAN AND COALITION OFFICIALS, IS HAILED AS A MAJOR BLOW TO THE INSURGENCY IN THE AREA.

OperationsSIGACTPublishedReportCasualty.Comments: INS Commander Ahmad Ibrahimi was killed as a result of a recent operation.

data.Title: (ENEMY ACTION) DIRECT FIRE RPT  Sar Rawza
data.Summary:
ON 061858JUN2017 LOCAL POLICE DEFENDED THEMSELVES AGAINST A LARGE ATTACK ON THEIR SECURITY CHECKPOINT, KILLING A REPORTED DOZEN INSURGENTS OUTSIDE OF MARZAK VILLAGE, SAR HOWZAH DISTRICT, AND PAKTIKA PROVINCE THURSDAY. THE INSURGENTS ATTACKED THE CHECKPOINT, LOCATED NEAR A GIRL'S SCHOOL, WITH SMALL ARMS FIRE AND ROCKET-PROPELLED GRENADES. THE LOCAL POLICE PARTNERED WITH THE NATIONAL ARMY AND COALITION SPECIAL OPERATIONS FORCES, QUICKLY RESPONDED TO THE ATTACK, REPELLING THE INSURGENTS AND FORCING TO FLEE SOUTH INTO THE MOUNTAINS. ADDITIONALLY, 3 LP MEMBERS TAKEN CAPTIVE BY THE INSURGENTS DURING THE ATTACK WERE RESCUED, RECEIVED MEDICAL TREATMENT AND ARE IN STABLE CONDITION. NO CIVILIANS WERE HARMED IN THE ENGAGEMENT.

BDA: 12 X INS KIA AND 3 X LOCAL POLICE KIA

COLLATOR COMMENT: BASED ON THE SAW HOWZAH DISTRICT AND PAKTIKA PROVINCE, THE MGRS LOCATION OF 42SWB0154557475 IS AN ESTIMATE OF THE REPORTED AREA.

data.Title: (FRIENDLY ACTION) CAS RPT  Sayid Karam
data.Summary:
ON 121928JUN2017, AFGHAN AND COALITION FORCES KILLED A NUMBER OF INSURGENTS DURING AN OPERATION IN SAYAD KARAM DISTRICT, PAKTIYA PROVINCE, TODAY. DURING THE OPERATION, THE SECURITY FORCE POSITIVELY IDENTIFIED THE MILITANTS ENGAGING IN INSURGENT ACTIVITY IN AN ISOLATED AREA AWAY FROM CIVILIANS. THE SECURITY FORCE CONDUCTED A PRECISION AIRSTRIKE, KILLING 5 INSURGENTS. A POST-STRIKE ASSESSMENT DETERMINED NO CIVILIANS WERE HARMED AND NO CIVILIAN PROPERTY WAS DAMAGED DURING THE OPERATION.

COLLATOR COMMENT: THE MGRS LOCATION OF 42SWC3607119873 IS GENERALIZED BASED OFF THE PAKTYA PROVINCE.

OperationsSIGACTPublishedReportCasualty.Comments: The security force conducted a precision airstrike, killing the insurgents during an operation.
